subject: JUnit 4.1 initial impressions

messageBody:
A week ago I downloaded JUnit 4.1 and started using it. The excellent
article, JUnit 4.0 in 10 minutes, was pretty much all I needed.

I'm hooked on this version. I wrote up my initial impressions with a
few examples at: http://schuchert.wikispaces.com/JUnit+4.x. If you are
so inclined, have a look and tell me what you think.

Thanks!

Brett
